imdb.plot outline: Some ancient candidates of TV Reality Show go abroad in another country to live together in a villa. Their goal is to break into their professional projects. During the TV show, the candidates will have challenges for have money to charities. Unfortunately, the candidates will confront and fight. At the end of the Reality TV show, there will be no winner because the TV Reality Show is only for their professional projects and for have money to charities.
